  {"message":
   "SSExactMajority/Protocol/Transition.lean:20:0: The module doc-string for a file should be the first command after the imports.\nPlease, add a module doc-string before `/-- Phase 4b: median decision (lines 12-18). Only changes `answer`. -/\ndef phase4_decide (n : ℕ) (b₀ b₁ : AgentState n) (x₀ x₁ : Opinion) : AgentState n × AgentState n :=\n  if n % 2 = 0 then\n    if b₀.rank.val + 1 = n / 2 ∧ b₁.rank.val + 1 = n / 2 + 1 then\n      if x₀ = x₁ then ({ b₀ with answer := opinionToAnswer x₀ }, { b₁ with answer := opinionToAnswer x₀ })\n      else ({ b₀ with answer := .outT }, { b₁ with answer := .outT })\n    else\n      if b₁.rank.val + 1 = n / 2 ∧ b₀.rank.val + 1 = n / 2 + 1 then\n        if x₁ = x₀ then ({ b₀ with answer := opinionToAnswer x₁ }, { b₁ with answer := opinionToAnswer x₁ })\n        else ({ b₀ with answer := .outT }, { b₁ with answer := .outT })\n      else (b₀, b₁)\n  else\n    let b₀ := if b₀.rank.val + 1 = ceilHalf n then { b₀ with answer := opinionToAnswer x₀ } else b₀\n    let b₁ := if b₁.rank.val + 1 = ceilHalf n then { b₁ with answer := opinionToAnswer x₁ } else b₁\n    (b₀, b₁)`.\n\nNote: This linter can be disabled with `set_option linter.style.header false`",
